citation: Vehicle and Traffic Amendment (Vehicle Inspection Fees) Act 2007 (Repealed) (Tas)
text:
Vehicle and Traffic Amendment (Vehicle Inspection Fees) Act 2007 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Vehicle and Traffic Amendment (Vehicle Inspection Fees) Act 2007 has been repealed by Schedule 1 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
